 />\n唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等我問下佢先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊聞 <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20150522/19156507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20150522%2F19156507&d=9%2BZN6Ff8PaoQpbDbzc4Ei8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=77b518e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20150522%2F19156507&h=0d2ba87f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20150522/19156507</a><br />\n<br />\n房屋署做擔保，不過冇H按，P按，廿五年，銀行唔係信你(朋友)，難聽啲係信房屋署"},{"pid":"500c8e0237e88b8408d0dbe0d66dd8442af44225","tid":296821,"uid":92936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"正常黎講應該係銀行同一二線財仔都唔會SO你／你朋友，但係居屋由房署做擔保，所以我估應該無問題 （好似係）<br />\n<br />\nBTW 不如問房署，我地唔係做房署<br />\n<br />\n再BTW 屌你／你個FD ，咁好彩抽到居屋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}